    "transliteration": [
      "Vajiba, Maharajna ek khubaj mota bhakta hata. Teo Sathvara samajna hata ane Vijapurma raheta hata. Teo badha sadhune premthi jamadta ane vastro aapta. Ekvar, temne sacha sadhuna guno ane Satsangna niyam samjhya, pachhi teo khubaj paka bhakta banya. Temne samjayu ke khota bavane jamadva ane vastro aapva nakama chhe, etle temne temne aavkarvanu bandh karyu.\nEkvar, Shriji Maharaj Mulji Brahmachari sathe Vajibana ghare padharya. Vajibae Shriji Maharajne kyareya joya nahota, etle teo temne olkhi shakya nahin. Maharaje temni shraddha ketli chhe te jova mate ghana chamatkaro batavya. Potani sarvagna shaktithi, temne rotla, khatlo ane gadlu mangya. Temne potana pag pipalana zadne adadya, chhata pan Vajibani Maharaj pratyeni shraddha jaray dagi nahin. Kharekhar to, temni shraddha vadhu majbut bani, bhale teo janta nahota ke Maharaj potej temna ghare mehman banine avya hata.\nMaharaj gaya pachhi thoda divasoma, Vajibae Gadhada jaine temna darshan karvanu nakki karyu. Tya, Maharaje temne puchhyu, “Tame aa charnarvindne olkho chho?” Vajibae javab apyo, “Maharaj! Hu to aaje pahelivar tamara darshan kari rahi chhu.” Maharaje kahyu, “Aa ej pag chhe je tamara pipalana zadne adya hata.” Ashcharyachakit thaine Vajiba bolya, “Oh Maharaj! Te divase tamej avya hata? Hu to tamne olkhi j na shaki. Ane me to tamari sathe khub kadkaithi vartan karyu.” Maharaj hasya ane Vajibane shanti aapta kahyu, “Hu to tari pariksha leva avyo hato. Tari shraddha jaray dagi nahin. Tara jeva bhakto bhale mari sathe kadkaithi varte, mane to tema pan khub anand thay chhe!” Je bhaktoni shraddha paki hoy chhe, teo Bhagwan pote pariksha le to pan potani nisthamanthi dagta nathi. Ava paka bhakto par Bhagwan potano prem varasave chhe.",
      "Ekvar, Shriji Maharaj Mulji Brahmachari sathe Vajibana ghare padharya. Vajibae Maharajne kyareya joya nahota, etle teo temne olkhi shakya nahin. Maharaje Vajibani shraddha ketli chhe te jova mate ghana chamatkaro batavya. Potani shaktithi temne rotla, khatlo ane gadlu mangya. Temne potana pag pipalana zadne adadya, chhata pan Vajibani Maharaj pratyeni shraddha jaray dagi nahin. Kharekhar to, temni shraddha vadhu majbut bani, bhale teo janta nahota ke Maharaj potej temna ghare mehman banine avya hata.",
      "Maharaj gaya pachhi thoda divasoma, Vajibae Gadhada jaine temna darshan karvanu nakki karyu. Tya, Maharaje temne puchhyu, “Tame aa charnarvindne olkho chho?” Vajibae javab apyo, “Maharaj! Hu to aaje pahelivar tamara darshan kari rahi chhu.”",
      "Maharaje kahyu, “Aa ej pag chhe je tamara pipalana zadne adya hata.”",
      "Ashcharyachakit thaine Vajiba bolya, “Oh Maharaj! Te divase tamej avya hata? Hu to tamne olkhi j na shaki. Ane me to tamari sathe khub kadkaithi vartan karyu.”",
      "Maharaj hasya ane Vajibane shanti aapta kahyu, “Hu to tari pariksha leva avyo hato. Tari shraddha jaray dagi nahin. Tara jeva bhakto bhale mari sathe kadkaithi varte, mane to tema pan khub anand thay chhe!”",
      "Je bhaktoni shraddha paki hoy chhe, teo Bhagwan pote pariksha le to pan potani nisthamanthi dagta nathi. Ava paka bhakto par Bhagwan potano prem varasave chhe."
    ]
