      "Aa samaye ek dukhhad ghatna bani. Gaayonu doodh dohti vakhte Narad ni mummy ne saape karadyo ane te mrutyu paami. Aathi aa nani umare Narad anaath bani gayo. Tene ghanivar rishione kaheta sambhalya hata ke Bhagwan j badhana mata-pita chhe. Teoe kahyu hatu ke temni prarthana karvathi dukh ane nakhushi dur thaay chhe. Naradne aa shabdo yaad aavya. Tethi ek savare vahela, tene potano tamburo lidho ane aashram chhodi didho. Te uttar disha ma, Himalaya tarf chalva laagyo.",
      "Te gaam pachhi gaam pasar karto gayo. Tene ghani nadio paar kari. Te parvato par chadyo. Chhevate te ek gaadh jangal ma praveshyo. Ahi ghana jangali praniyo raheta hata. Chhata te daryo nahi. Te chalto rahyo, jya sudhi te ek sundar ane shant nadi paase na pahochyo. Tene tena thanda, taajgibharyaa paani ma snaan karyu. Tene thodu paani gaaline pidhu. Pachhi tene aaspaas joyu ane ek vishaal pipal nu jhaad joyu. Teni thandi chhaya niche te palanthi vaaline betho, aankho bandh kari ane prarthana karva laagyo, “He Bhagwan! Tame mara pita ane mari mata chho. Mane tamari god ma lo.”",
